efs_file_system_id.description: EFS file system id used for SQLite persistence

google_oauth_secret_arn.description: Secrets Manager secret ARN containing client_secret.json

az_count.description: Number of AZs to use (2 recommended)

container_port.description: Port the application listens on inside the container

desired_count.description: Number of tasks to run (keep 1 if using SQLite on EFS)

domain_name.description: (Optional) Domain name for HTTPS (e.g., app.example.com). If empty, ALB DNS name is used and HTTP listener is created.

google_oauth_client_secret_json.description: Contents of Google OAuth client_secret.json (JSON string). Stored in Secrets Manager.

health_check_path.description: ALB target group health check path

hosted_zone_id.description: (Optional) Route53 hosted zone id for domain_name. Required if domain_name is set.

image_tag.description: Container image tag to deploy from ECR

project_name.description: Project name used for resource naming
